Transmutation
Level: Cleric 5
Components : V,S
Casting Time: 1 Action
Range: Medium
Target: All enemies in a 20ft radius
Duration: 1 minute / Level
Save: Will Negates
SR: Yes
Meta Magic: Still, Silent, Extend

